      • linkEntities

        @Deprecated
public static boolean linkEntities(CoalesceEntity entity1,
                                                ELinkTypes linkType,
                                                CoalesceEntity entity2,
                                                boolean updateExisting)
        Deprecated. this methods swallows the CoalesceException therefore you should use one of the others.
        Links two entities together with a default Unclassified classification and Locale.US. If updateExisting is true then the first linkage found between the two entities with the same ELinkTypes will be updated instead of creating a new linkage.
        Parameters:
        entity1 - the first entity to link
        linkType - the type of linkage to create between the two entities.
        entity2 - the second entity to link
        updateExisting - whether to update an existing linkage.
        Returns:
        true if successful.

      • linkEntities

        public static void linkEntities(CoalesceEntity entity1,
                                ELinkTypes linkType,
                                CoalesceEntity entity2,
                                String modifiedBy,
                                String modifiedByIp,
                                String label,
                                boolean updateExisting,
                                boolean isReadOnly,
                                boolean canUpdateReadOnly)
                         throws CoalesceException
        Links two entities together. If updateExisting is true then the first linkage found between the two entities with the same ELinkTypes will be updated instead of creating a new linkage.
        Parameters:
        entity1 - the first entity to link
        linkType - the type of linkage to create between the two entities.
        entity2 - the second entity to link
        modifiedBy - the identifier representing who modified the linkage.
        modifiedByIp - the IP address of the computer used to make the modification.
        label -
        updateExisting - whether to update an existing linkage.
        isReadOnly - specifies whether the linkage should be made as read only.
        canUpdateReadOnly - specifies whether the link can be updated if it's already marked as read only.
        Throws:
        CoalesceException
